{
  "id": "69aadd67041ab2b364a0d000",
  "title": "私を構成する9つのアニメ",
  "created": 1772805480,
  "updated": 1772890292,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69aadd67041ab2b364a0d000",
      "text": "私を構成する9つのアニメ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805480,
      "updated": 1772805480
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadd6700000000004c2eba",
      "text": "from [2026/03/06]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805480,
      "updated": 1772805480
    },
    {
      "id": "69aade0700000000004c2ede",
      "text": "[私を構成する9つのアニメ https://tlpt-telepath.github.io/9-animes/]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805639,
      "updated": 1772805640
    },
    {
      "id": "69aade0800000000004c2ee0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805640,
      "updated": 1772805640
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf100000000004c2ed5",
      "text": " 流行りにのって[私を構成する9つのアニメ]選んでみた [これ https://tlpt-telepath.github.io/9-animes/][terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2ed6",
      "text": " \t\t[https://gyazo.com/f00ad3cd21ed062afe5bf76caa14225c]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2ed7",
      "text": " \t\t\t選外で、エヴァ、ブラックラグーン、ヴァイオレットエヴァガ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2ed8",
      "text": " \t\t\t9個選ぶの難しいな[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2ed9",
      "text": " \t\t\t9個も思いつかなかった[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2eda",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t手元のリスト見たらたくさんあるが、特に選べない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2edb",
      "text": " \t\t\t\tかわいいアニメ並べたくなるかも（これはこれで欲望って意味で「私を構成する」になるか）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2edc",
      "text": " \t\t私を構成する9つの漫画はアクセス集中でやる前に終わってしまっていた [via. https://x.com/UgokuWare/status/2029735293855879308]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddf200000000004c2edd",
      "text": " \t\t[音楽の方 https://tlpt-telepath.github.io/9-musics/]はちょっと考えたけど無理だった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805618,
      "updated": 1772805618
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadd6700000000004c2ebb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805480,
      "updated": 1772805610
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadd6700000000004c2ebc",
      "text": " 思いついた順[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805480,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadd6700000000004c2ebd",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/0449e931a3deea1ff99c6be2eb3cfaf1]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805480,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddbe00000000004c2ec8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805567,
      "updated": 1772805567
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddbf00000000004c2eca",
      "text": " こんな感じかな？[koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805567,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddc000000000004c2ecb",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/8aef1657a3337bbd8f21ea85742c8727]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805569,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddc000000000004c2ecc",
      "text": "   自分とかなり近そう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805569,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaddc000000000004c2ecd",
      "text": "    ということはこの中で見てないやつを見ればよいのだろう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805569,
      "updated": 1772805607
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadddf00000000004c2ecf",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805600
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadde000000000004c2ed0",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/257fe4fa5cc3058106849d5b38574be6]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805600
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadde000000000004c2ed1",
      "text": "\t\t中央の圧が強い",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805600
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadde000000000004c2ed2",
      "text": "\t\t人のをみて思い出したが最後のはモノノ怪じゃなくてウテナだったな",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805600
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadde000000000004c2ed3",
      "text": "\t\t 人生三大アニメ、セーラームーン、ウテナ、[スティーブン・ユニバース]かも",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805839
    },
    {
      "id": "69aadde000000000004c2ed4",
      "text": "\t\t  セーラームーン、正直話は全然覚えてないけどファッションと変身バンクが好き",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772805600,
      "updated": 1772805600
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26940000000000cdd974",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889748,
      "updated": 1772889748
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26940000000000cdd975",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889748,
      "updated": 1772889749
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26a00000000000cdd979",
      "text": " こうかなぁ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889760,
      "updated": 1772889762
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26950000000000cdd977",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/0454c60b28d4432570d287d1b92b55b1]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889749,
      "updated": 1772889752
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26a70000000000cdd97a",
      "text": " 私を構成する、と言われると難しい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889767,
      "updated": 1772889777
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26b60000000000cdd97b",
      "text": " 子どもの頃に見てたやつとか感動したやつの比重が若干高まる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889783,
      "updated": 1772890292
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26980000000000cdd978",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889752,
      "updated": 1772889752
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac26950000000000cdd976",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772889749,
      "updated": 1772889749
    }
  ]
}